oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Discussion Paper Series in Finance
Collection
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Akimov, Alexandr
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Discussion Paper Series in Finance represents work in progress on a range of finance and financial planning issues from the Department of Accounting, Finance and Economics. The papers are also published to the Research Papers in Economics (RePEc) web database of working papers, journals articles and software components.
